name: Jump Besi Jump
overview: Jump Besi Jump game that has just been released for Commodore Amiga. Created by Cobe, Koyot 1222, D4rk 3lf, code based on Graham Humphreys "Downfall" and the music module is a cover of DJ Nick's "Running Snake". Little game about our dog Besi who loves to jump sometimes like a rabbit through the tall grass but mostly freestyle 360s. In this platform game , start the game with the Button ,then you only need to steer no Button. Jump up and get Stars ,example = if you are on level 3 you need to get three stars to beat the level. Anoying Bird disturb you in the game , you can also jump on the Bird , don't fall down Jump !
